content: As you cross the bridge, you can harvest some Licorice on the other side, and look to the left to spot a large archway in the distance, with a whirling black tornado even further left in a canyon separating the Fright Cliffs from the Crouching Tiger Temple.

As you cross the bridge, you can harvest some Licorice on the other side, and look to the left to spot a large archway in the distance, with a whirling black tornado even further left in a canyon separating the Fright Cliffs from the Crouching Tiger Temple.
